creator: Recreation App
descriptionHtml:
Explore our 6 core categories (Art, Dance, Games, Music, Soul and Sports) to discover and save on local Group Activities, Events and Private Teachers, specifically tailored for Adults!

Rediscover your passion. Find a hobby. Learn a new skill. Connect with friends. Meet new people. Your Inner Child is Calling!

Within each category you'll find listings for Activities and Teachers.
You'll see the listings closest to your location first, and within each listing you'll find Ratings, Reviews, Coupons, Contact and Enrollment info.

Want to keep track of the listings you're interested in? Just click the bookmark icon on the listing and find your favorites in the drop down of your category page.

Loved a class? Found a great teacher? Be sure to add your personal ratings and reviews.

Inspire & get Inspired! Be sure to share your experiences with the Recreation community.
descriptionShort: Recreation - Local Activities and Private Teachers for Adults
